ed="T" n="0721a16"/><persName key="A000140">釋勿提提羼魚</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A000140">蓮華精進</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000047816">屈支城</placeName>人<lb
ed="T" n="0721a17"/>也，即<placeName key="PL000000047816">龜茲國</placeName>，亦云<placeName key="PL000000047816">丘慈</placeName>，正曰<placeName key="PL000000047816">屈支</placeName>。時<name>唐</name>使<persName key="A009152">車<lb
ed="T" n="0721a18"/>奉朝</persName><ptr target="#n385"/>到<ref target="#PL000000047816" type="place">彼土</ref>，城西門外有<placeName key="PL000000047806">蓮華寺</placeName>，<persName key="A000140">進</persName>居此<lb
ed="T" n="0721a19"/>中，號<persName key="A000140">三藏<anchor xml:id="beg0721sgsz3"/>苾芻<anchor xml:id="end0721sgsz3"/></persName>。<persName key="A009152">奉朝</persName>至誠祈請，開譯<name>梵</name>夾，<lb
ed="T" n="0721a20"/>傳歸<placeName key="PL000000000083">東夏</placeName>。<persName key="A000140">進</persName>允之，遂譯出《十力經》<ptr target="#n190"/>，可用東<lb
ed="T" n="0721a21"/>紙三幅<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g722"/>成一卷，是佛在<placeName key="PL000000048396">舍衛國</placeName>說。<placeName key="PL000000047826">安西</placeName>境<lb
ed="T" n="0721a22"/>內有<placeName key="PL000000047803">前踐山</placeName>，山下有伽藍，其水滴溜，成音<lb
ed="T" n="0721a23"/>可愛。彼人每歲一時，采綴其聲，以成曲調。<lb
ed="T" n="0721a24"/>故耶婆瑟雞<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>用為羯鼓曲名<ptr target="#n386"/>，樂工最<lb
ed="T" n="0721a25"/>難其杖撩之術。<persName key="A000140">進</persName>寺近其滴水也。其經<lb
ed="T" n="0721a26"/>是沙門<persName key="A009152">悟空</persName>同《十地》<ptr target="#n191"/>、《迴向輪經》<ptr target="#n193"/>共十一卷，齎<lb
ed="T" n="0721a27"/>進。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015327" notAfter-iso="+0805-09-04"><name>貞元</name>中</date>請編入藏，值<persName key="A001417">圓照</persName>續錄，故述其<lb
ed="T" n="0721a28"/>由。</p>
